Scott Adams: The Democrat Party needs to be ripped out by the roots

@ScottAdamsSays “Two days ago I would have said the healthiest thing for the country is that there are two strong political parties battling it out, in a war of ideas. 
But you know who else thought that?

@VigilantFox I will NEVER allow someone to rewrite Charlie Kirk’s legacy. I’m disgusted that they tried this both-sides-ism bullshit. I will call it out every time.

Do not make peace with evil.

Also, Chris Cuomo ended his show tonight with an on-air apology to me and Charlie for this. Good.

